snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 1 – Invasions Season 3 Trailer
snippet.description:
An unbearable freeze has befallen our timeline. The Season of the Cryomancer has begun in #MK1 and will run till February 13. Bring a jacket.

Get your copy and jump into Invasions today: https://www.mortalkombat.com/purchase

It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a new era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
